N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 84.5 - Term and validity of registration

State Regulations

Each approved registration shall be valid only with
respect to the licensee to whom it is issued and shall not be transferable. The
term of the registration shall coincide with that of the holder's license and
shall be renewed annually. Notes
